    • Uses of IDocAnalyzer in analyzers

      Subinterfaces of IDocAnalyzer in analyzers 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  ICategorizer
      Interface for IAnalyzer objects that work with categories.
      Classes in analyzers that implement IDocAnalyzer 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  CategoriesCalculator
      This is the main IAnalyzer that is designed to identify categories.
      class  CategoriesSetter
      This IAnalyzer simulates calculation of categories.
      class  LanguageAnalyzer
      This IAnalyzer identifies the language of the document
      class  LanguageAnalyzerDefault
      This IAnalyzer identifies the language of both elemental and standard document
      class  StatisticsGatherer
      This IAnalyzer gathers statistics about the input data and the resulting analysis
      class  TDMatrixPreparator
      This IAnalyzer prepares a term-document matrix to be used by clustering algorithms
      class  TfIdfCalculator
      This IAnalyzer finalizes the words weights normalization by updating data for all documents
      class  TfIdfPreparator
      This IAnalyzer prepares data for the normalization with the help of the TF-IDF algorithm - it counts words and calculates their weights with the help of the provided TF and IDF functions
